  <h1>Burr Grinder Settings for Espresso (2026): A Repeatable Dial-In Workflow</h1>
  <p class="lead">Getting better espresso shots is mostly about running the same process every time. This guide walks through a practical baseline, fast correction loop, and maintenance rhythm so burr grinder settings for espresso become predictable instead of frustrating.</p>

  <HeroSteps
    title="Dial In Espresso in 4 Repeatable Steps"
    subtitle="Keep variables controlled so each grinder adjustment gives clear feedback"
